dc_title_s: County and municipality map of New Jersey: political boundaries revised to December 31, 1939
dc_description_s: New Jersey. Division of Conservation and Development. Division of Geology and Topography. Atlas Sheet no. 39 (1942) (County/municipality) New Jersey Geological Survey. Political boundaries as of June 1, l924. In upper margin: Atlas sheet no. 39. Surveyed 1977-1887. Base compiled and engraved 1910-1912. From original surveys based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey; C. C. Vermeule, Topographer. The shore lines of tidal waters are mainly from the U.S.C.& G. Survey. Boudary lines revised by L. P. Plummer, Topographic Engineer.
dc_publisher_s: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1939.
